friendi.sh
=========
post to friendica over API with bash and curl
by tony baldwin
http://tonyb.us/friendish
https://free-haven.org/profile/tony

Friendica posting script with xposting control
Post to Friendica from your bash terminal,
control crossposting to external networks.

License: 
released according to the terms of the GPL v. 3 or later.

Installation:
run the install.sh script

bash/english
